OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FThe ceasefire between Lebanon and
OL,7,FIsrael has been extended by three
OL,8,Fweeks, Donald Trump has said.
OL,10,FThe president made the announcement on
OL,11,Fhis Truth Social platform on Thursday,
OL,12,Fsaying the deal had been agreed upon
OL,13,Fduring a meeting with Israeli and
OL,14,FLebanese officials in the Oval Office.
OL,16,FHe said the meeting went "very well"
OL,17,Fand that the US had offered to help
OL,18,FLebanon protect "itself from
OL,19,FHezbollah".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
