OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777021560
OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FHezbollah, the militant group that is
OL,7,Fbased in Lebanon and was the combatant
OL,8,FIsrael was fighting, has not commented
OL,9,Fon the announcement.
OL,11,FTrump also said he was going to host
OL,12,Fboth the prime minister of Israel and
OL,13,Fthe president of Lebanon in the near
OL,14,Ffuture.
OL,16,FThe initial ten-day ceasefire, which
OL,17,Ftook effect last Friday, had been due
OL,18,Fto expire on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
