OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FSpeaking before the ceasefire
OL,7,Fextension, Lebanese President Joseph
OL,8,FAoun said he hoped to lay the
OL,9,Fgroundwork for further negotiations
OL,10,Fwith Israel.
OL,12,FHe said the aim of the talks was to
OL,13,F"fully" stop Israeli attacks, the
OL,14,Fwithdrawal of Israeli troops from
OL,15,FLebanon, the release of Lebanese
OL,16,Fprisoners held in Israel, the
OL,17,Fdeployment of Lebanese troops along
OL,18,Fthe border and the beginning of the
OL,19,Freconstruction process.
