OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FHezbollah has previously rejected any
OL,7,Fkind of wider negotiation with Israel
OL,8,Fand has vowed not to abide by any
OL,9,Fagreement the Lebanese government
OL,10,Fmakes with its southern neighbour.
OL,12,FSince the ceasefire came into effect
OL,13,Flast week, there have been multiple
OL,14,Fviolations by both sides.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday, Amal Khalil, a well-
OL,17,Fknown Lebanese journalist covering
OL,18,Fsouthern Lebanon, was killed by an
OL,19,FIsraeli strike.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
