OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLebanese health officials said the
OL,12,FIsraeli military opened fire on an
OL,13,Fambulance that responded to the scene,
OL,14,Fpreventing rescuers from reaching her.
OL,15,FHer body was pulled from the rubble of
OL,16,Fa collapsed building several hours
OL,17,Flater.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
