OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FThe Israeli military denied that it
OL,7,Fhad deliberately targeted journalists
OL,8,For fired on rescuers, but the case
OL,9,Fsparked widespread anger in Lebanon
OL,10,Fahead of the Washington talks.
OL,12,FThe latest Israel-Hezbollah war has
OL,13,Fkilled around 2,300 people in Lebanon,
OL,14,Fincluding hundreds of women and
OL,15,Fchildren, and displaced over 1 million
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,FThe developments come as wider US
OL,19,Fdiplomacy in the region remains
OL,20,Ffragile.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
