OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FIn earlier remarks to reporters at the
OL,7,FWhite House, Trump said he did not
OL,8,Fwant to rush into a deal with Iran,
OL,9,Fadding: "I don't want to rush myself."
OL,11,FHe described Iran's leadership as
OL,12,Fbeing "in turmoil", as talks between
OL,13,FWashington and Tehran remain in limbo.
OL,15,FEarlier this week, Trump extended a
OL,16,Fseparate ceasefire between the US and
OL,17,FIran after at least two ships were
OL,18,Fattacked in the Strait of Hormuz.
