OL,3,CIsrael-Lebanon ceasefire extended by
OL,4,Cthree weeks, Trump says
OL,6,FThe US president said the move
OL,7,Ffollowed a request from Pakistan,
OL,8,Fwhich has been mediating in the
OL,9,Fconflict, to give Tehran time to
OL,10,Fpresent a "unified proposal" to end
OL,11,Fthe war.
